Reconsidering Systems-Based Practice: Advancing Structural Competency, Health 
Equity, and Social Responsibility in Graduate Medical Education.

Castillo EG(1), Isom J(2), DeBonis KL(3), Jordan A(4), Braslow JT(5), Rohrbaugh 
R(6).

Author information:
(1)E.G. Castillo is a psychiatrist, Los Angeles County Department of Mental 
Health, and assistant professor, Jane and Terry Semel Institute for Neuroscience 
and Human Behavior at UCLA, Center for Social Medicine and Humanities, 
Department of Psychiatry and Biobehavioral Sciences, David Geffen School of 
