Medical comorbid diagnoses among adult psychiatric inpatients.

Goldman ML(1), Mangurian C(2), Corbeil T(3), Wall MM(4), Tang F(5), Haselden 
M(4), Essock SM(6), Frimpong E(5), Mascayano F(3), Radigan M(5), Schneider M(7), 
